data.description: Cane Island Retreat. Enjoy unparalleled sweeping tidal creek views of the Beaufort River. This magnificent quintessential Lowcountry style home defines the ultimate in timeless design and fine custom construction. The open kitchen is perfect for the most discerning of chefs. It includes a dining area, huge island, Dacor gas range, Sub-Zero fridge, built in oven, wine fridge and ice maker. Impress your guests with the formal dining room that boasts highly detailed craftsmanship in the custom millwork or by grilling up a feast in the covered grilling porch and entertaining outdoors at the paved patio with fire-pit overlooking the water.
